* K&K New Hire + CE Farm

fields.description:
_Context_: This customer now has 4 packets in his site 2 from CA and 2 from OR (in the next few days we will add from TX and FL). And CA is where they are hiring the most (they are doing it right now) so they would like these packets to be at the top of the list. 

So we need to reorganize them in the following order:

# [CA Spanish - Everde|https://app.useanvil.com/org/ganaz/w/ca-spanish-everde] | [https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1454|https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1454|smart-link] 
# [CA English - Everde|https://app.useanvil.com/org/ganaz/w/ca-english-everde] | [https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1455|https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1455|smart-link] 
# [OR Spanish - Everde|https://app.useanvil.com/org/ganaz/w/or-spanish-everde-1] | [https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1583|https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1583|smart-link] 
# [OR English - Everde|https://app.useanvil.com/org/ganaz/w/or-english-everde] | [https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1582|https://app.ganaz.com/internal-support-tool/Packet/Editor?packetId=1582|smart-link] 

IF you have questions, please reach me.
fields.customfield_10131: They were asking us to correct this asap, as CA people hire more and there are more chances of selecting the wrong packets

comments.body: thank you, I have already verified it. You can close the ticket.
